#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hacking &appname;"
msgstr "Programiranje &appname;"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:4
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the spirit of Free Software, you are welcome to hack on &appname; as much "
"as you like. You should be able to write scripts to import, export, or "
"modify data very easily. This chapter gives you more information about doing "
"that."
msgstr ""
"V duhu proste programske opreme ste dobrodošli, da programirate za &appname; "
"kolikor hočete. Morali bi biti sposobni zelo enostavno pisati skripte za "
"uvoz, izvoz ali spreminjanje podatkov. To poglavje vam ponuja več informacij "
"o tem."

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Format"
msgstr "Format datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default &appname; data file is a zip archive, normally with a <literal "
"role=\"extension\">.tc</literal> file extension. Inside the archive is a top-"
"level <filename>tellico.xml</filename> file. Images may be included inside "
"the <filename>images/</filename> folder in the archive, or they may be "
"included in the &XML; data directly in a base64 encoding. Images may also be "
"saved inside the application data folder, in which case, they are not in the "
"data file at all. &appname; can also load the &XML; file, by itself, "
"uncompressed."
msgstr ""
"Privzeta podatkovna datoteka za &appname; je arhiv zip, običajno s pripono "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.tc</literal>. Znotraj arhiva je datoteka "
"<filename>tellico.xml</filename> najvišje ravni. Slike so lahko vključene v "
"mapo <filename>images/</filename> v arhivu ali pa so vključene v datoteko "
"&XML; podatke neposredno v kodiranju base64. Slike so lahko shranjene tudi v "
"podatkovni mapi aplikacije, v tem primeru pa sploh niso v podatkovni "
"datoteki. &appname; lahko tudi sama po sebi naloži nestisnjeno &XML; "
"datoteko."

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid "&XML; Data"
msgstr "&XML; podatki"

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collection"
msgstr "Zbirka"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: hacking.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<![CDATA[\n"
"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n"
"<!DOCTYPE tellico PUBLIC \"-//Robby Stephenson/DTD Tellico V11.0//EN\" "
"\"http://periapsis.org/tellico/dtd/v11/tellico.dtd\">\n"
"<tellico xmlns=\"http://periapsis.org/tellico/\" syntaxVersion=\"11\">\n"
" <collection title=\"My Books\" type=\"2\">\n"
" </collection>\n"
"</tellico>\n"
"]]>"
msgstr ""
"<![CDATA[\n"
"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n"
"<!DOCTYPE tellico PUBLIC \"-//Robby Stephenson/DTD Tellico V11.0//EN\" "
"\"http://periapsis.org/tellico/dtd/v11/tellico.dtd\">\n"
"<tellico xmlns=\"http://periapsis.org/tellico/\" syntaxVersion=\"11\">\n"
" <collection title=\"My Books\" type=\"2\">\n"
" </collection>\n"
"</tellico>\n"
"]]>"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The file begins with the required &XML; declaration and encoding, followed "
"by the doctype. When a new field type is added or additional properties are "
"set on the default fields, the doctype DTD version is incremented. &appname; "
"is always able to open and read any previous DTD version, but will save "
"files in the current version. The DTD location does point to an actual DTD "
"file."
msgstr ""
"Datoteka se začne z zahtevanim &XML; deklaracijo in kodiranje, ki ji sledi "
"tip dokumenta. Ko je dodana nova vrsta polja ali nastavljene dodatne "
"lastnosti za privzeta polja, se različica doctype DTD poveča. &appname; "
"vedno lahko odpre in prebere katero koli prejšnjo različico DTD, vendar bo "
"shranil datoteke v trenutno različico. Lokacija DTD kaže na dejansko "
"datoteko DTD."

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The top-level element is a <markup>&lt;tellico&gt;</markup> element, "
"containing the default namespace declaration and the syntax version of the "
"file, which should always match the DTD."
msgstr ""
"Element najvišje ravni je element <markup>&lt;tellico&gt;</markup>, ki "
"vsebuje deklaracijo privzetega imenskega prostora in različico sintakse "
"datoteke, ki se mora vedno ujemati z DTD."

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <markup>&lt;tellico&gt;</markup> element contains one <markup>&lt;"
"collection&gt;</markup> element. Multiple collections are ignored, for now. "
"The <markup>title</markup> attribute contains the collection title, while "
"the <markup>type</markup> specifies what kinds of entries are contained in "
"the collection. The allowable types are in <link linkend=\"collection-type-"
"values\">listed in a later section</link>. An optional <markup>entryTitle</"
"markup> attribute may be used to specify the title of the entries for a "
"custom collection, and should be plural."
msgstr ""
"Element <markup>&lt;tellico&gt;</markup> vsebuje en element <markup>&lt;"
"collection&gt;</markup>. Več zbirk je za zdaj prezrtih. Atribut "
"<markup>title</markup> vsebuje naslov zbirke, medtem ko <markup>type</"
"markup> določa, katere vrste vnosov vsebuje zbirka. Dovoljene vrste so <link "
"linkend=\"collection-type-values\">navedene v kasnejšem razdelku</link>. "
"Izbirni atribut <markup>entryTitle</markup> se lahko uporabi za določitev "
"naslova vnosov za zbirko po meri in mora biti množinski."

