#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&appname; will include all the default fields for a collection if the first "
"field element has the name <emphasis>_default</emphasis>. For "
"<emphasis>Paragraph</emphasis>, <emphasis>Table</emphasis>, or "
"<emphasis>Image</emphasis> fields, the field category should be identical to "
"the field title."
msgstr ""
"&appname; bo vključeval vsa privzeta polja za zbirko, če ima prvi element "
"polja ime <emphasis>_default</emphasis>. Za polja <emphasis>Odstavek</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis>Tabela</emphasis> ali <emphasis>Slika</emphasis> mora "
"biti kategorija polja enaka naslovu polja."

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The type of field is given in the type attribute of the field element. The "
"value is equal to the <type>FieldType</type> enum value in <filename>src/"
"field.h</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Tip polja je podan v atributu tipa elementa polja. Vrednost je enaka "
"vrednosti enum <type>FieldType</type> v <filename>src/field.h</filename>."

