#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The field may have different flags set, given as a bitwise OR'd value in the "
"flags attribute on the field element. The flag for preventing the user from "
"deleting a field is intended for such things as the citation key for "
"bibliographic entries."
msgstr ""
"Polje ima lahko nastavljene različne zastavice, podane kot bitna vrednost "
"ALI v atributu zastavic na elementu polja. Zastavica, ki uporabniku "
"preprečuje brisanje polja, je namenjena stvarem, kot je ključ navedbe za "
"bibliografske vnose."

