#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hidden Configuration Options"
msgstr "Možnosti skrite konfiguracije"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&appname; has some additional configuration options that are not visible in "
"the <interface>Configuration Dialog</interface>. They are not important "
"enough to warrant cluttering the dialog with more settings, but as they "
"represent options which may appeal to various users, the application does "
"read them from the configuration file."
msgstr ""
"&appname; ima nekaj dodatnih konfiguracijskih možnosti, ki niso vidne v "
"<interface>konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu</interface>. Niso dovolj "
"pomembne, da bi upravičile natrpanje pogovornega okna z več nastavitvami, a "
"ker predstavljajo možnosti, ki bi lahko pritegnile različne uporabnike, jih "
"aplikacija prebere iz konfiguracijske datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The settings for &appname; are saved in a file in the user's home folder, "
"typically <filename>~/.config/tellicorc</filename>. Within that file, "
"settings are put in groups, which appear with bracketed names, such as "
"[General Options]. To add a setting to the <emphasis>General Options</"
"emphasis> group, find the line in the settings file with that group name. If "
"it does not appear, then create it yourself by adding a line saying [General "
"Options]. Then, the setting can be added underneath the group name."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve za &appname; se shranjujejo v datoteko v domači mapi uporabnika, "
"in sicer praviloma v <filename>~/.config/tellicorc</filename>. Znotraj te "
"datoteke so nastavitve razvrščene v skupine, ki se prikažejo z imeni v "
"oklepajih, kot je [General Options]. Če želite dodati nastavitev v skupino "
"<emphasis>Splošne možnosti</emphasis>, poiščite vrstico v datoteki z "
"nastavitvami z imenom te skupine. Če se ne prikaže, ga ustvarite sami, tako "
"da dodate vrstico [General Options]. Nato lahko nastavitev dodate pod ime "
"skupine."

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "[General Options]"
msgstr "[General Options]"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These settings should be placed in the <emphasis>General Options</emphasis> "
"group."
msgstr ""
"Te nastavitve je treba postaviti v skupino <emphasis>Splošne možnosti - "
"General Options</emphasis>."

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid "Max Icon Size"
msgstr "Največja velikost ikone"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The maximum size of the icons in the <interface>Icon View</interface> may be "
"changed with this setting. The default value is 96. The size must be in the "
"range of 32 to 512."
msgstr ""
"S to nastavitvijo lahko spremenite največjo velikost ikon v "
"<interface>Pogled ikon</interface>. Privzeta vrednost je 96. Velikost mora "
"biti v območju od 32 do 512."

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:231 hacking.docbook:246 hacking.docbook:261
#: hacking.docbook:285 hacking.docbook:304 hacking.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example"
msgstr "Primer"

#. Tag: userinput
#: hacking.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Max Icon Size=128"
msgstr "Max Icon Size=128"

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid "Icon Cache Size"
msgstr "Velikost predpomnilnika ikon"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The maximum numbers of icons cached in memory may be changed with this "
"setting. The default value is 1000."
msgstr ""
"S to nastavitvijo lahko spremenite največje število ikon, ki so predpomnjene "
"v pomnilniku. Privzeta vrednost je 1000."

#. Tag: userinput
#: hacking.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid "Icon Cache Size=100"
msgstr "Icon Cache Size=100"

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid "Image Cache Size"
msgstr "Velikost predpomnilnika slike"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The maximum amount of memory in bytes used for caching all the images may be "
"changed with this setting. The default value is 512 MiB."
msgstr ""
"Največjo količino pomnilnika v bajtih, ki se uporablja za predpomnjenje vseh "
"slik, je mogoče spremeniti s to nastavitvijo. Privzeta vrednost je 512 MiB."

#. Tag: userinput
#: hacking.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "Image Cache Size=256000000"
msgstr "Image Cache Size=256000000"

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid "[Options - bibtex]"
msgstr "[Možnosti - bibtex]"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These settings should be placed in the <emphasis>Options - bibtex</emphasis> "
"group."
msgstr ""
"Te nastavitve bi morali postaviti v skupino <emphasis>Možnosti - bibtex</"
"emphasis>."

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "lyxpipe"
msgstr "lyxpipe"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting is for the location of the lyxpipe for sending bibliographic "
"citations. It should not include the <literal role=\"extension\">.in</"
"literal> suffix."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev je za lokacijo lyxpipe za pošiljanje bibliografskih citatov. "
"Ne sme vsebovati pripone <literal role=\"extension\">.in</literal>."

#. Tag: userinput
#: hacking.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid "lyxpipe=$HOME/.lyx/lyxpipe"
msgstr "lyxpipe=$HOME/.lyx/lyxpipe"

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "[File Reader Options]"
msgstr "[File Reader Options]"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These settings should be placed in the <emphasis>File Reader Options</"
"emphasis> group."
msgstr ""
"Te nastavitve je treba postaviti v skupino <emphasis>File Reader Options</"
"emphasis>."

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preview Size"
msgstr "Preview Size"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "This setting is for the maximum size of the generated file preview."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev je za največjo velikost ustvarjenega predogleda datoteke."

#. Tag: userinput
#: hacking.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preview Size=523"
msgstr "Preview Size=523"

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid "Multi-Disc Options"
msgstr "Več-diskovne možnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"musicbrainz\">MusicBrainz</link>, <link linkend=\"discogs"
"\">Discogs</link>, and <link linkend=\"itunes\">iTunes</link> data sources "
"can fetch multi-disc album information, specifying which tracks each disc "
"contains. By default, the track lists are inserted into separate field, one "
"for each disc. Prior to version 4.0, the track lists were combined. This "
"option provides the pre-4.0 behavior on an individual data source level. Add "
"it to each <emphasis>Data Source</emphasis> section where it is desired."
msgstr ""
"Viri podatkov <link linkend=\"musicbrainz\">MusicBrainz</link>, <link "
"linkend=\"discogs\">Discogs</link> in <link linkend=\"itunes\">iTunes</link> "
"lahko pridobijo informacije o albumih z več diski, pri čemer navajajo, "
"katere skladbe vsebuje vsak disk. Privzeto so seznami skladb vstavljeni v "
"ločena polja, po eno za vsak disk. Pred različico 4.0 so bili seznami skladb "
"združeni. Ta možnost zagotavlja delovanje pred različico 4.0 na ravni "
"posameznega vira podatkov. Dodajte jo v vsak razdelek <emphasis>Data Source</"
"emphasis>, kjer jo želite."

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Split Tracks By Disc"
msgstr "Split Tracks By Disc"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Setting this to <emphasis>false</emphasis> reverts to pre-4.0 behavior where "
"the tracks are collapsed into a single track list."
msgstr ""
"Če to nastavite na <emphasis>false</emphasis>, se vrne na delovanje pred "
"različico 4.0, kjer so skladbe strnjene v en sam seznam skladb."

#. Tag: userinput
#: hacking.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "Split Tracks By Disc=false"
msgstr "Split Tracks By Disc=false"

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bibtex Character Translation"
msgstr "Prevod znakov Bibtex"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When bibtex files are imported or exported, certain characters are "
"translated between their TeX equivalents and the Unicode characters. Those "
"character mappings are contained in the <filename>bibtex-translation.xml</"
"filename> file, located in the installation data directory. The mappings can "
"be modified, as desired. The key element contains the Unicode character, and "
"the string elements within contain the TeX equivalents, which may be a one-"
"to-many mapping. The first one is the one used when exporting to bibtex."
msgstr ""
"Ko so datoteke bibtex uvožene ali izvožene, se nekateri znaki prevedejo med "
"njihovimi ekvivalenti TeX in znaki Unicode. Te preslikave znakov so v "
"datoteki <filename>bibtex-translation.xml</filename>, ki se nahaja v imeniku "
"namestitvenih podatkov. Preslikave je mogoče po želji spreminjati. Ključni "
"element vsebuje znak Unicode, elementi niza znotraj pa vsebujejo ekvivalente "
"TeX, ki so lahko preslikava ena proti mnogo. Prvi je tisti, ki se uporablja "
"pri izvozu v bibtex."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: hacking.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<![CDATA[\n"
"  <key char=\"À\">\n"
"    <string>{\\`A}</string>\n"
"    <string>\\`{A}</string>\n"
"  </key>\n"
"]]>"
msgstr ""
"<![CDATA[\n"
"  <key char=\"À\">\n"
"    <string>{\\`A}</string>\n"
"    <string>\\`{A}</string>\n"
"  </key>\n"
"]]>"

